    <headline>Polar low ongoing, yellow level, B3, B4, 03 February 07:00 UTC to 03 February 14:00 UTC.</headline>
    <description>Thursday morning a polar low has formed at 75.40N and 17.00E. North easterly severe gale force 9 is expected northwest of the center of the low. The polar low will move slowly west-north west during the day and dissipate Thursday afternoon.</description>
